      • computeHazardCommon

        public static void computeHazardCommon(RegionalZone zone,
                       Evu evu)
        Calculates the Hazard of LightLpMpb and SevereLpMpb. The first if block is used when lodge pole is the dominant species or occurs with one other species, the else if block when lodgepole pine is a minor component occurrring with two other species.
        Parameters:
        zone - is a RegionalZone.
        evu - is an Evu, the Evu to calculate the hazard for.
